name: What is Prescribed?
description: This piece is dear to my heart. “What is prescribed” is influenced by the reactions I had received when I tell people I am diagnosed, especially around 10 years ago. Recently, I have noticed there has been more acceptance in the community around mental health and I wanted to create a two-part piece where there has been a cultural reset to how we react. So please take a marker and write something down for someone who may come out to you. It will help those who are still afraid to be open with what they are going through.
